name: What'stheworkout
0:
”Alexa, ask workout generator for today's workout”
”give me a workout”
”give me todays workout”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: workout generator
des: This app turns Alexa into an in house functional fitness coach! Backed with an ever growing archive of workouts, Alexa chooses today's WOD for you so you don't have to. Simply ask her for today's workout and she will let you know what to do when you get to the gym.
